$
f(x_{1},x_{2},x_{3})=-3x_{1}^2+6x_{1}x_{3}-3x_{3}^2\\
A=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
-3 & 0 & 3\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
3 & 0 & -3\end{array}\right)
\left|\begin{array}{ccc}
-3-\lambda & 0 & 3\\
0 & 0-\lambda & 0\\
3 & 0 & -3-\lambda\end{array}\right|=-\lambda^3-6\lambda^2=0\\
\lambda_{1}= 0; \ кр-2;\\
\lambda_{2}= -6; \ кр-1;\\

\lambda_{1}= 0;\\
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
-3 & 0 & 3\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
3 & 0 & -3\end{array}\right) \sim 
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & -1\\
0 & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow\\
\begin{cases}
x_{1}=x_{3}\\
x_{2}=x_{2}\\
x_{3}=x_{3}\end{cases} \Rightarrow \vec a_{1}=(1,0,1); \ \vec a_{2}=(0,1,0); (кр-2)\\

\lambda_{2}= -6;\\
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
3 & 0 & 3\\
0 & 6 & 0\\
3 & 0 & 3\end{array}\right) \sim 
\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & 1\\
0 & 1 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow\\
\begin{cases}
x_{1}=-x_{3}\\
x_{2}=0\\
x_{3}=x_{3}\end{cases} \Rightarrow \vec a_{3}=(-1,0,1);\\
\\

\vec a_{1} \cdot \vec a_{2} = 0 \Rightarrow \vec a_{1} \perp \vec a_{2};\\
\vec a_{1} \cdot \vec a_{3} = 0 \Rightarrow \vec a_{1} \perp \vec a_{3};\\
\vec a_{2} \cdot \vec a_{3} = 0 \Rightarrow \vec a_{2} \perp \vec a_{3};\\
$
$
Нормирование:\\
|\vec a_{1}|=\sqrt{1+1}=\sqrt{2}\\
|\vec a_{2}|=1\\
|\vec a_{3}|=\sqrt{1+1}=\sqrt{2}\\

\vec a_{1}=(\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}, 0, \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}})\\
\vec a_{2}=(0, 1, 0)\\
\vec a_{3}=(-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}, 0, \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}})\\

P=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & 0 & -\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\\
0 & 1 & 0\\
\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} & 0 & \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\end{array}\right)\\
f(y_{1},y_{2},y_{3})=0 \cdot y_{1}^2 +  0 \cdot y_{2}^2 -6y_{3}^2
